1893
Life A
1₂2128
F645
(S)
PREFACE.
BELIEVING Song to be one of God's appointed
ways of spreading the gospel, we send this little
messenger forth in His name.
"I am the light of the world:
he that followeth me shall not
walk in darkness, but shall have
the Light of Life."-JOHN VII: 12.
EDW. S. FOGG.
T. W. BARKER.
EMORY UNIVERSITY
THEOLOGY LIBRARY
